<div class="section">
  <h3>7.9 后端核心实现（Django）</h3>
  <h4>7.9.1 统一响应体与分页结构</h4>
  <pre class="small"><code>server/comm/BaseView.py
class BaseView(View):
  def parasePage(pageIndex, pageSize, pageTotal, count, data):
    return {'pageIndex': pageIndex, 'pageSize': pageSize, 'pageTotal': pageTotal, 'count': count, 'data': data}
  def success(msg='处理成功'):
    return HttpResponse(json.dumps({'code': 0, 'msg': msg}), content_type='application/json; charset=utf-8')
  def successData(data, msg='处理成功'):
    return HttpResponse(json.dumps({'code': 0, 'msg': msg, 'data': data}), content_type='application/json; charset=utf-8')
  def warn(msg='操作异常，请重试'):
    return HttpResponse(json.dumps({'code': 1, 'msg': msg}), content_type='application/json; charset=utf-8')
  def error(msg='系统异常'):
    return HttpResponse(json.dumps({'code': 2, 'msg': msg}), content_type='application/json; charset=utf-8')
</code></pre>
  <p>所有视图均应返回 `code==0` 代表成功，前端拦截器据此统一处理状态与消息。</p>

  <h4>7.9.2 URL 路由总览</h4>
