  <h4>7.9.3 试卷与练习：数量校验与随机组卷</h4>
  <pre class="small"><code>server/comm/ExamUtils.py
class CheckPractiseTotal():
  def check(projectId):
    data_0 = CheckPractiseTotal.qryPractises(0, projectId)  # 选择题
    data_1 = CheckPractiseTotal.qryPractises(1, projectId)  # 填空题
    data_2 = CheckPractiseTotal.qryPractises(2, projectId)  # 判断题
    data_3 = CheckPractiseTotal.qryPractises(3, projectId)  # 编程题
    return (CheckPractiseTotal.check_0(data_0) & CheckPractiseTotal.check_1(data_1)
            & CheckPractiseTotal.check_2(data_2) & CheckPractiseTotal.check_3(data_3))

class MakeExam():
  def make(projectId):
    data_0 = MakeExam.qryPractises(0, projectId)
    data_1 = MakeExam.qryPractises(1, projectId)
    data_2 = MakeExam.qryPractises(2, projectId)
    data_3 = MakeExam.qryPractises(3, projectId)
    nums_0 = MakeExam.make_0(data_0)
    nums_1 = MakeExam.make_1(data_1)
    nums_2 = MakeExam.make_2(data_2)
    nums_3 = MakeExam.make_3(data_3)
    return {'item_0': nums_0, 'item_1': nums_1, 'item_2': nums_2, 'item_3': nums_3}
</code></pre>
  <p>该工具类用于生成随机题号集合与校验科目题量是否足够，避免发布后出现“题量不足”导致的运行时异常。</p>

  <h4>7.9.4 练习/任务/错题 核心模型</h4>
  <pre class="small"><code>server/app/models.py
class StudentPracticeLogs(models.Model):
  student = models.ForeignKey(Users, on_delete=models.CASCADE, db_column='student_id', to_field='id')
  paper = models.ForeignKey(PracticePapers, on_delete=models.CASCADE, db_column='paper_id')
  startTime = models.CharField(max_length=19, db_column='start_time')
  endTime = models.CharField(max_length=19, db_column='end_time', null=True)
  score = models.FloatField(default=0.0)
  accuracy = models.FloatField(default=0.0)
  status = models.CharField(max_length=20, default='in_progress')

class StudentPracticeAnswers(models.Model):
  practiceLog = models.ForeignKey(StudentPracticeLogs, on_delete=models.CASCADE, db_column='practice_log_id')
  practise = models.ForeignKey(Practises, on_delete=models.CASCADE, db_column='practise_id')
  studentAnswer = models.TextField(null=True)
  isCorrect = models.BooleanField(null=True)
  score = models.FloatField(default=0.0)

class WrongQuestions(models.Model):
  student = models.ForeignKey(Users, on_delete=models.CASCADE, db_column='student_id', to_field='id')
  practise = models.ForeignKey(Practises, on_delete=models.CASCADE, db_column='practise_id')
  source = models.CharField(max_length=20)  # task/exam/practice
  wrongAnswer = models.TextField(null=True)
  correctAnswer = models.TextField(null=True)
  analysis = models.TextField(null=True)
</code></pre>
  <p>错题记录用于支撑“错题专项”再练；日志与答案模型支撑“继续练习/统计/导出”。</p>
</div>

<div class="section">
  <h3>7.10 前端核心实现（Vue + Axios）</h3>
  <h4>7.10.1 Axios 拦截器与统一错误处理</h4>
  <pre class="small"><code>client/src/utils/http.js
// POST：非 FormData 默认 qs.stringify；下载/纯文本直接透传
// 响应：code==0/1 正常返回；其他弹出 Notice；/exit/ 静默处理
service.interceptors.response.use(
  success => {
    if (typeof success.data === 'string' || success.request?.responseType === 'blob') return success
    if (success.data.code == 0 || success.data.code == 1) return success.data
    const url = success?.config?.url || ''
    if (url.includes('/exit/')) { return { code: 0, msg: '退出成功', data: {} } }
    Notice.error({ duration: 3, title: success.data.msg });
    return Promise.reject(success.data)
  },
  error => {
    const url = error?.config?.url || ''
    if (url.includes('/exit/')) { return Promise.resolve({ code: 0, msg: '退出成功', data: {} }) }
    Notice.error({ duration: 3, title: '系统异常，请求中断' });
    return Promise.reject(error)
  }
)
</code></pre>
  <p>退出接口无论后端响应如何都静默成功，前端统一清理会话，避免“退出弹错”。</p>

  <h4>7.10.2 API 层与导出/下载</h4>
  <pre class="small"><code>client/src/api/index.js
// 学生练习与导出
export function getStudentPracticePapers(token) { return http.get('/practicepapers/student/', { params: { token: token || '' } }) }
export function startPractice(token, paperId) { return http.post('/studentpractice/start/', { token: token || '', paperId }) }
export function exportPracticeLogs(token) { return http.get('/studentpractice/export/', { params: { token }, responseType: 'blob' }) }
export function exportPracticeAnswers(logId) { return http.get('/studentpractice/export_answers/', { params: { logId }, responseType: 'blob' }) }

// 题目导入/导出
export function importAdminQuestions(formData) { return http.post('/admin/questions_import/', formData, { headers: { 'Content-Type': 'multipart/form-data' } }) }
export function exportAdminQuestions(filters) { return http.post('/admin/questions_export/', filters, { responseType: 'blob' }) }
</code></pre>

  <h4>7.10.3 路由与菜单（含 AI 页）</h4>
  <pre class="small"><code>client/src/router/index.js
children: [
  { path: 'aiScoring', name: 'aiScoring', component: require("../views/pages/aiScoring.vue").default },
  { path: 'aiQuestionGenerator', name: 'aiQuestionGenerator', component: require("../views/pages/aiQuestionGenerator.vue").default }
]
</code></pre>

  <h4>7.10.4 顶部导航：静默退出</h4>
  <pre class="small"><code>client/src/components/nav.vue
exit(this.$store.state.token)
  .finally(() => {
    this.$store.commit('clearToken'); this.$store.commit('clearMenus');
    sessionStorage.clear(); window.location.href = '/';
  });
</code></pre>
  <p>配合拦截器的 `/exit/` 特判，确保任何异常情况下都能“无提示地”退出到登录页。</p>
</div>

<div class="section">
  <h3>7.11 进阶说明与可扩展点</h3>
  <ul>
    <li><strong>AI 接口重试/提示</strong>：前端建议统一封装 `withRetry`，在 AI 高负载时给出“繁忙，正在重试”文案。</li>
    <li><strong>编程题沙箱</strong>：后续可引入 Docker + 资源限制 + 测试用例，实现安全判题与部分得分。</li>
    <li><strong>学习分析</strong>：按知识点/题型/难度维度出图表（趋势/雷达），沉淀学生画像。</li>
    <li><strong>Excel(XLSX) 支持</strong>：在 CSV 基础上扩展为 XLSX 导入导出，提升可用性。</li>
  </ul>
</div>

<div class="section">
  <h3>8. Critical Evaluation</h3>
  <h4>8.1 Problems/difficulties encountered and solutions</h4>
  <ul>
    <li>Compile errors from method separators → fixed.</li>
    <li>Select runtime error due to non-string values → enforced String values/labels.</li>
    <li>Inconsistent success checks → unified to code==0.</li>
    <li>Logout error popups → silent handling for /exit/.</li>
    <li>AI variability → standardized prompts, frontend retry, backend fallback.</li>
  </ul>
  <h4>8.2 Limitations of the proposed system</h4>
  <ul>
    <li>Programming questions not yet executed in a secure sandbox with resource limits.</li>
    <li>No async queue yet for long AI jobs.</li>
    <li>Learning analytics dashboard minimal (trends/radar pending).</li>
    <li>Limited formal evaluation (accuracy/latency/cost vs baseline).</li>
  </ul>
</div>

<div class="section">
  <h3>9. Project Progress and Schedule</h3>
  <h4>9.1 Proposed project schedule update</h4>
  <ul>
    <li>W1–2: Setup, DB alignment, base CRUD</li>
    <li>W3–4: Practice/Tasks/Exams flows, CSV import/export</li>
    <li>W5–6: AI scoring & question generation (MVP), error handling unification</li>
    <li>W7–8: Stability pass, menus, exports, wrong-question drills</li>
    <li>W9–10 (next): Programming sandbox (Docker), partial scoring, task queue</li>
    <li>W11–12 (next): Analytics dashboard; evaluation; deployment scripts</li>
  </ul>
  <h4>9.2 Completed and future deliverables</h4>
  <p><strong>Completed:</strong> Multi-role UI; practice/tasks; AI scoring/generation MVP; CSV I/O; wrong-question drills; unified interceptors and value typing; docs.</p>
  <p><strong>Planned:</strong> Sandbox + partial scores; Celery/Redis; analytics dashboards; formal evaluation; Docker Compose deployment.</p>
  <h4>9.3 Tools, facilities and hardware</h4>
  <p>Dev: Node.js, npm, Python 3.x, Django, MySQL, Git. Optional: Docker/Compose. Accounts: OpenAI/OpenRouter key.</p>
  <h4>9.4 Dev vs Prod environment</h4>
  <p>Dev: Windows 10, local Django & Vue servers, local MySQL. Prod target: Linux VM/Containers; Nginx; Docker Compose; .env config.</p>
</div>

